title: For Sale:  Double-Action Only (DAO) FN Five Seven 5.7 w/ AMMO (LEO MODEL)
postcontent: his is an EXCELLENT CONDITION, Extremely RARE Original, FIRST edition, FN Five Seven 5.7.The first variant Five-seven DAO pistol was originally restricted by FN to law enforcement and military customers use ONLY. It is double-action only with a trigger pull of 4.5 to 6.5 daN (10 to 14 lbf) and NO manual safety device. It has a pebbled grip pattern, smoothly-contoured accessory rail, low profile fixed sights and a circular-shaped trigger guard designed to improve gloved use. It does not have a slide release and the slide is not serrated as on newer variants, but a portion of the slide is instead slightly concave to aid grasping. The original Five-seven pistols were shipped with only two (2) 20 round magazines. This pistol comes in the original FNH hard case with operator’s instructions/manual, cleaning kit, and (2) 20 round magazines. PLUS ~ 500 rounds SS198LF LEO/Military Ammo (10 boxes).
